72
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:14,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, Joon Gu.</font>

73
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Lama tidak bertemu.</font>

74
00:06:16,530 --> 00:06:17,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana pekerjaanmu?</font>

75
00:06:17,530 --> 00:06:19,540
