115
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:58,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian bukan berandal.</font>

116
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:02,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu anggota geng. Jangan membuat malu preman lainnya.</font>

117
00:10:02,990 --> 00:10:05,430
