<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan hanya mengharapkan keberuntungan dan nasib baik.</font>

127
00:11:11,690 --> 00:11:14,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian harus menyesali dosa-dosa kalian.</font>

128
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:21,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei.</font>

129
00:11:23,570 --> 00:11:26,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Jin Seok memerintahkan kalian untuk menghabisiku?</font>

130
00:11:29,310 --> 00:11:30,450
