133
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:39,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia adalah anak buah Pak Cheon.</font>

134
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:41,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Namanya Lee Jin Seok.</font>

